A minimalistic architectural diagram rendered as an elegant blueprint-style illustration showing three floating geometric platforms connected by glowing translucent data streams. The lowest platform holds a stylized cylindrical database shape in deep amber, the middle platform displays a sleek hexagonal processing core in steel blue, and the top platform features a crystalline dome representing a web interface in soft white. The platforms are arranged in an ascending diagonal composition against a clean navy background with subtle grid lines. Each connection between layers pulses with flowing particles suggesting data movement. The overall aesthetic is clean, modern, and technical without any visible text or labels, using only shape and color to convey the layered architecture of connected systems.
